{"tid":225994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普:金正恩是一個「相當聰明的人」，如果能與他會面會感到榮幸。","createTime":"2017-05-02T08:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T13:28:37.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69ee2a6bb60f04f2bfbfe653c010f9b361128a53","tid":225994,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.images.dailystar.co.uk/dynamic/1/photos/433000/620x/Donald-Trump-and-Kim-Jong-un-564288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.dailystar.co.uk%2Fdynamic%2F1%2Fphotos%2F433000%2F620x%2FDonald-Trump-and-Kim-Jong-un-564288.jpg&h=70d5b078&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，如果時機適合，他願意與北韓最高領導人金正恩舉行會面。<br />\n<br />\n近幾周對北韓措辭強硬的特朗普，星期一在白宮表示，「他（金正恩）是一個相當聰明的人。如果與他會面是一件可行之事，我肯定會這麼做，並且會感到榮幸，但前提是情況要允許&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/161213150939-trump-kim-jong-un-split-amanpour-exlarge-169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.cdn.cnn.com%2Fcnnnext%2Fdam%2Fassets%2F161213150939-trump-kim-jong-un-split-amanpour-exlarge-169.jpg&h=e075cea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人斯派塞補充指，「情況允許」意味著很多事情，包括北韓須即時停止挑釁行為，會面才有機會成事，但強調現時時機未到。<br />\n<br />\n斯派塞表示，朝鮮半島局勢持續緊張，北韓對美國以及地區盟友構成嚴重的潛在安全威脅。特朗普將始終把保護美國的國家安全作為首要目標。他強調，從目前的情況看，美朝領導人之間不存在會面的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/78/590x/North-Korea-brands-Donald-Trump-s-offer-to-meet-Kim-Jong-un-as-insincere-nonsense-673137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F78%2F590x%2FNorth-Korea-brands-Donald-Trump-s-offer-to-meet-Kim-Jong-un-as-insincere-nonsense-673137.jpg&h=85af8597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝鮮半島局勢持續升級，特朗普曾揚言不惜用一切手段，包括軍事行動處理北韓問題。但他近日在接受採訪時態度放軟，表示希望通過外交手段解決北韓問題。但他亦強調，與北韓發生大規模衝突的可能性是存在的。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指，美國會眾議院本周將就是否對北韓施加新的經濟制裁進行討論，新制裁可能針對北韓航運業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dingo.care2.com/pictures/petition_images/petition/082/293307-1492018184-wide.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdingo.care2.com%2Fpictures%2Fpetition_images%2Fpetition%2F082%2F293307-1492018184-wide.jpg&h=5dceef79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8a78f41c5da0b098ea074fd45c05e2f14c98b65","tid":225994,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/world/%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e9%a1%98%e6%84%8f%e8%88%87%e9%87%91%e6%ad%a3%e6%81%a9%e6%9c%83%e6%99%a4/ar-BBABEP0?li=BBqiJuS&amp;ocid=SL5MDHP#image=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F%25e7%2589%25b9%25e6%259c%2597%25e6%2599%25ae%25e9%25a1%2598%25e6%2584%258f%25e8%2588%2587%25e9%2587%2591%25e6%25ad%25a3%25e6%2581%25a9%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%2599%25a4%2Far-BBABEP0%3Fli%3DBBqiJuS%26ocid%3DSL5MDHP%23image%3D1&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4ef54c6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/world/%e7%89%b9%e6%9c%97%e6%99%ae%e9%a1%98%e6%84%8f%e8%88%87%e9%87%91%e6%ad%a3%e6%81%a9%e6%9c%83%e6%99%a4/ar-BBABEP0?li=BBqiJuS&amp;ocid=SL5MDHP#image=1</a>"},{"pid":"de87c44dbd47c3bb13277488d4a1d07877542688","tid":225994,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.skynews.com.au/content/dam/skynews/news/politics/international/2016/03/04/skynews_1027620247.jpg/jcr:content/renditions/skynews.img.1200.745.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skynews.com.au%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fskynews%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Finternational%2F2016%2F03%2F04%2Fskynews_1027620247.jpg%2Fjcr%3Acontent%2Frenditions%2Fskynews.img.1200.745.jpeg&h=43e2deba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"125b8f93de8113a764f5f2c98fa791d59c4b184f","tid":225994,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.abc.net.au/news/image/836