噉㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n不單止侵侵欣賞佢，可能連普京都欣賞佢，金仔同普京真係可能做到fd，普京突然出兵其實係防止中共入侵北韓，中共反應太慢。"},{"pid":"19af97b89536c245f4b49635d05c46fc9e98f49f","tid":225994,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"244ac1d1c8547a46d209be4170f7c33d95e2fdf3","tid":225994,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d377b7194b56a547e7cbf75c02d8bd60c7e2c5f0","tid":225994,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家先識得欣賞金仔遲唔遲d</blockquote><br />\n可能特朗普一早知佢唔簡單，所以佢先叫中共出馬，試下佢是否有真材實料，連侵侵都估唔到中共根本唔係佢嘅對手，中共比金仔嚇到冇咩反應，加上之後普京站佢台，派兵到邊境防止中共入侵北韓，看來侵侵要親自會一會這位強者。"},{"pid":"a3a0125aa606f96645e0594634c7402033f3c56c","tid":225994,"uid":106408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"特朗普真係個少數講老實話既人"},{"pid":"16b287952a2c2718fb9d5131329592c7211e811e","tid":225994,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特朗普真係個少數講老實話既人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前唔記得咗佢啱啱先講話邊一個係偉大領袖話？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6d3a8e937a21d66416db8d3ab8cff21cb41c77","tid":225994,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果這步棋，搞到北韓成為美國盟國，佢真係前無古人後冇來者。</blockquote><br />\n唔係想收服左北韓跟住再槍頭對住中國掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下一步收復埋中共<br />\n再下一步收復俄羅斯<br />\n<br />\n不戰而屈人之兵"},{"pid":"5a8853cbf5c0f0a6e0ba22e0b00c3ca8d5f7d172","tid":225994,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T12:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚完習棋王撚金仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撚到好撚亂啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ab868eabd